{"tid":2307225,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"劉康促印度停港引渡協議","createTime":"2020-12-01T04:55:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T05:05:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5d101fb2834e79215023740a8c09a15f280f73d7","tid":2307225,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/BFPJRQJK3BDCPKGKWFLWSKCYWE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FBFPJRQJK3BDCPKGKWFLWSKCYWE%2F&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0nIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=beca824f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201201%2FBFPJRQJK3BDCPKGKWFLWSKCYWE%2F&h=20c5789a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201201/BFPJRQJK3BDCPKGKWFLWSKCYWE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n劉康促印度停港引渡協議<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_CsbTGG3KLSo9B4Jz_To6SSRfFQ=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N6RKKXSJKJDLDGZSVWTWVWIANE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_CsbTGG3KLSo9B4Jz_To6SSRfFQ%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN6RKKXSJKJDLDGZSVWTWVWIANE.jpg&h=47b175a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】涉違港版國安法被通緝的香港公開大學學生劉康（圖）昨致函印度外務大臣蘇濟生（Subrahmanyam Jaishankar），呼籲印度鑑於香港公民自由受侵犯，加強制裁香港與中國政府，並停止與香港的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n劉康指出，印度與港的引渡協議嚴重威脅港僑、海外台灣人及世界上所有支持自由的人。他表示港版國安法導致多人出於政治原因被捕、控告、監禁，又導致很多港人流亡。他又指即使身處香港及中國以外，由於國安惡法適用於任何人及任何地方，因此只要批評香港及中國政府，即使是印度人也會受國安法威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n籲制裁中港官員<br />\n<br />\n劉康稱不少英聯邦國家已停止與香港的引渡協議，包括英國、澳洲、加拿大、新西蘭，希望印度作為英聯邦一分子，亦會停止與香港的引渡協議。<br />\n<br />\n他感謝印度限制一些不安全的中國公司及產品，又請求印度進一步限制威脅自由。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n劉康為香港效益主義黨主席，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"0e5061ce16764637d859d51e50046264f671885f","tid":2307225,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T04:56:36.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a0dc49c18064882fcebe19123e6e871cd73d63","tid":2307225,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:04:39.000Z","msg":"有個文子星引渡緊，點會而家取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2839cc8a76fdd4b5e4d948c88514fb8092013c5a","tid":2307225,"uid":85406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}